{"talk":{"id":2464,"name":"Linus Torvalds: The mind behind Linux","description":"Linus Torvalds transformed technology twice -- first with the Linux kernel, which helps power the Internet, and again with Git, the source code management system used by developers worldwide. In a rare interview with TED Curator Chris Anderson, Torvalds discusses with remarkable openness the personality traits that prompted his unique philosophy of work, engineering and life. \"I am not a visionary, I'm an engineer,\" Torvalds says. \"I'm perfectly happy with all the people who are walking around and just staring at the clouds ... but I'm looking at the ground, and I want to fix the pothole that's right in front of me before I fall in.\"","slug":"linus_torvalds_the_mind_behind_linux","recorded_at":"2016-02-17 00:00:00","published_at":"2016-04-08 16:00:29","updated_at":"2021-04-13 21:28:30","viewed_count":3856560,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":377,"name":"TED2016"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/798940cde334a3a3672104290616e56a2dd9e49a_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/798940cde334a3a3672104290616e56a2dd9e49a_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/798940cde334a3a3672104290616e56a2dd9e49a_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/798940cde334a3a3672104290616e56a2dd9e49a_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/d560e7d7d695293217875d2db6fbb35b31fc1991_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/LinusTorvalds_2016-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":10676232,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/LinusTorvalds_2016-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":29480397,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/downlo